OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny haar in east soon becoming
OL,6,Fconfined to the immediate coast to
OL,7,Fleave a largely dry day with sunny
OL,8,Fspells, perhaps just the odd shower
OL,9,Fover the mountains. Very warm or hot
OL,10,Finland but much cooler on the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Outbreaks of heavy
OL,14,Fthundery rain, risk of torrential
OL,15,Fdownpours and hail, spread southeast
OL,16,Fovernight. Drier later across
OL,17,FPerthshire and Stirlingshire.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
