OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,6,Fbrightness but outbreaks of heavy
OL,7,Fthundery rain near the east coast
OL,8,Fspread back northwest across the area
OL,9,Fthrough the day. Much cooler than
OL,10,Frecently.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,13,Fstart Saturday, but cloud increasing
OL,14,Fwith showery rain later. Sunday and
OL,15,FMonday see sunny spells and showers,
OL,16,Fwith a fresh southwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
